---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import { SITE_CONFIG } from '../config';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Affiliate Disclosure - InSpotGO"
  description="Learn about InSpotGO's affiliate relationships and how we maintain editorial independence while earning commissions."
>
  <div class="container content-page">
    <h1>Affiliate Disclosure</h1>

    <p class="last-updated">Last Updated: March 1, 2026</p>

    <section>
      <h2>Introduction</h2>
      <p>
        InSpotGO ({SITE_CONFIG.url}) participates in affiliate marketing programs for software and SaaS products.
        When you click certain links on our site and sign up for or purchase a product, we may receive
        a commission at no additional cost to you.
      </p>
      <p>
        This disclosure is provided in accordance with the Federal Trade Commission's (FTC)
        <a href="https://www.ftc.gov/legal-library/browse/16-cfr-part-255" target="_blank" rel="noopener">16 CFR Part 255: Guides Concerning the Use of Endorsements and Testimonials in Advertising.</a>
      </p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Affiliate Programs We Participate In</h2>
      <p>
        We participate in affiliate programs offered by software companies and SaaS providers directly
        and through affiliate networks. These may include, but are not limited to:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>Direct affiliate programs with individual SaaS companies (e.g. monday.com, HubSpot, Notion, ClickUp, Canva)</li>
        <li>PartnerStack network partners</li>
        <li>Impact.com network partners</li>
        <li>ShareASale network partners</li>
        <li>CJ Affiliate (Commission Junction) network partners</li>
      </ul>
      <p>
        We do <strong>not</strong> participate in Amazon Associates or hardware product affiliate programs.
        InSpotGO focuses exclusively on software and SaaS tools.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>How Affiliate Links Work</h2>
      <p>
        When you click an affiliate link and complete a purchase or sign-up, the company pays us a commission.
        For SaaS products, commissions typically range from <strong>10% to 50%</strong> of the subscription value,
        and are often recurring for the duration of your subscription.
      </p>
      <p>
        <strong>Important:</strong> You never pay more by using our affiliate links. Affiliate relationships
        have zero influence on our editorial recommendations.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Our Editorial Independence</h2>
      <p>
        Affiliate relationships do not influence our editorial decisions. Our commitment to you:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Honest Reviews:</strong> We provide unbiased analysis highlighting both strengths and weaknesses of every tool.</li>
        <li><strong>No Pay-to-Play:</strong> Companies cannot pay for positive reviews or higher rankings.</li>
        <li><strong>User-First Recommendations:</strong> We only recommend tools we believe genuinely benefit our readers, regardless of commission rates.</li>
        <li><strong>Transparent Updates:</strong> Reviews are updated regularly to reflect product changes and better alternatives.</li>
        <li><strong>Clear Identification:</strong> Affiliate links are clearly disclosed on all relevant pages.</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Types of Affiliate Compensation</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Pay-Per-Sale:</strong> We earn a percentage when you purchase through our links.</li>
        <li><strong>Pay-Per-Lead:</strong> We may earn a fee when you sign up for free trials through our links.</li>
        <li><strong>Recurring Commissions:</strong> For SaaS subscriptions, we typically earn ongoing commissions for as long as you remain a customer — which is the most common model for the tools we cover.</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Product Testing & Reviews</h2>
      <p>When possible, we test tools directly through free trials or owned accounts. When we haven't personally tested a tool, we:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Conduct thorough research from multiple credible sources</li>
        <li>Analyze verified user reviews on G2, Capterra, Trustpilot, and Reddit</li>
        <li>Compare features and positioning against direct competitors</li>
        <li>Clearly state in our review when direct testing was not performed</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Your Support</h2>
      <p>
        Using our affiliate links supports InSpotGO at no extra cost to you. Commissions allow us to:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>Keep all content free and accessible</li>
        <li>Invest in thorough product research and testing</li>
        <li>Keep reviews updated as tools evolve</li>
        <li>Expand coverage to more software categories</li>
      </ul>
      <p>We genuinely appreciate your support.</p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Questions?</h2>
      <p>
        Contact us at <a href="mailto:{SITE_CONFIG.contact.email}">{SITE_CONFIG.contact.email}</a>
        or visit our <a href="/contact">Contact page</a>.
        For editorial standards, see our <a href="/editorial-policy">Editorial Policy</a>.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="legal-notice">
      <h2>Legal Notice</h2>
      <p>
        This disclosure is provided in good faith for general information purposes only.
        {SITE_CONFIG.legalEntity} makes no warranties about the completeness, reliability,
        or accuracy of this information.
      </p>
    </section>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .content-page { max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 2rem 1rem; }
  h1 { font-size: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; color: var(--color-text); }
  .last-updated { color: var(--color-text-light); font-size: 0.9rem; margin-bottom: 2rem; }
  section { margin: 3rem 0; }
  h2 { font-size: 1.75rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: var(--color-text); }
  h3 { font-size: 1.25rem; margin-top: 2rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; color: var(--color-text); }
  p { margin-bottom: 1rem; line-height: 1.7; color: var(--color-text-light); }
  ul { margin: 1rem 0; padding-left: 2rem; }
  li { margin-bottom: 0.75rem; line-height: 1.7; color: var(--color-text-light); }
  a { color: var(--color-primary); text-decoration: none; }
  a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }
  .legal-notice { background: var(--color-bg-alt); padding: 1.5rem; border-left: 4px solid var(--color-primary); margin-top: 3rem; }
  .legal-notice p { margin: 0; font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--color-text-light); }
  @media (max-width: 768px) { h1 { font-size: 2rem; } }
</style>
